Xen Command
===========

cat /sys/hypervisor/properties/capabilities				-->>   To check hypervisor properties installed on OS.

xm list           # List all domains
xm list vm1       # List status of a single VM
xm list vm1 -l    # Details for a VM 
xm create vm1     # Starts/Creates a VM
xm reboot vm1     
xm shutdown vm1
xm destroy vm1

xm network-list vm1

xm console vm1     # Open console to VM (escape like telnet)

xm info            # HV infos
xm top             # Monitor HV and domains
xm log             # View HV log

xm dominfo
xm vcpuinfo
xm nodeinfo
